      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, so i'm working on this character for our story. they're like... a digital consciousness that's starting to realize everything they are is just code that's being scheduled for deletion. they feel so heavy and useless, like they never really existed at all. if they just let the deletion happen and stop fighting it... would that even matter? like, does it even matter if they go?",
